name: Flat bed
description: 3 budded setts are used to plant in the end to end and the furrow is covered by 5-7 cm of soil and field is leveled by planking

name: Ring pit
description: Cane setts are placed in the triangle in pits and covered with soil

name: Mechanical whole planter
description: to plant whole cane with mechanical planter

name: Bud planting
description: Sugarcane buds with half of its stalk planted in small polyphone sleeves filled with organic manure and soil and after they sprouted out and they can be transplanted in the main field
